Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:06.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:22.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:23.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:27.92,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.39,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:36.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:43.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:53.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:59.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:06.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:13.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:21.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those goddesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are there three of them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:54.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but they also dared to\nsubject me to utter humiliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:02:02.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time around I'll show you\nthe true power of a First Class Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:10.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it...the throbbing\nenergy of your collective joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But all that will end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:16.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, all you'll know will be\nthe agony of a living hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}TARGET: MARLLER\NATTACK MODE: DEMON{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:49.82,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Misfortune Arrives,\nand the Tea-Stalk Stands Upright?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, I'm resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:59.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But for crying out loud...I can't\neven get them to notice when I appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am, a demon, and I'm\nup to my ears in misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:08.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To think that so much joy is\nconcentrated around this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:13.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him miserable.\NMiserable beyond belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:17.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mercilessly...undeniably miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:23.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's settled...\nit's somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:30.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the time has come\nfor me to put this to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With this Ultimate Last-resort\NWeapon in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:37.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...victory is as good as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:42.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Belldandy.\NNot to mention Keiichi Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:51.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking them head-on will only\ninvite more outside interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:54.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, what should I do? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, that was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:03.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for another great breakfast!\NSorry I keep imposing on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you're welcome\nto come over any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing every girl should have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:13.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a big brother with a girlfriend\nwho's gorgeous and a great cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:22.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get a move on or\nyou're gonna be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:26.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't have class until\nthe afternoon today. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:33.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...she's Keiichi's sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can put her to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Marller.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your lucky day. I'm about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help! It's a ghost!{\i0}\NToday's your lucky day. I'm about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help! It's a ghost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:56.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a ghost!\nI'm a respectable demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:00.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing\nI'm after here...your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Help! It's a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:13.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another...\nI'm claiming your body for my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-n-n...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess I was just hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Megumi, you know that's bad\nmanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:32.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's isn't a thing\nin this room worth anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not her! That's not Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:41.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!\NWho the hell are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:47.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Such...such power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:48.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is who the hell I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:56.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that mark...it's the\nmark of a first-class demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:04.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just lie there\nfor the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:07.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From here on in, I'm Megumi Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A test drive, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what the Seniors\nwant me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:24.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since our next race is coming up soon.\nIt's just that they're really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:29.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's going to be\na lot of prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Found you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That you, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:47.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look on your face?\NBig Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:51.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?\NYou're creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You always call me ''Kei-chan'',\nfor god's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:04.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Kei-chan!\nI was just kidding around, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:08.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, I thought you said\nyou didn't have class until later?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...well...the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:18.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi is always so\nfull of life, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I put up a double shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:33.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That Belldandy doesn't\nhave a clue it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:39.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can accomplish my goal!\nI'm going to give you two a taste of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:43.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Using my Ultimate Last-resort Weapon...\nfeared even by demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is now time to break\nthe seal of Evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Demon-god Senbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am most honored to be summoned by\nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:07.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Senbei, the God of Poverty, has received\nyour call and is at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...but you're so puny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Non, non, non...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:15.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the No. 1 elite God of Poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't be fooled\nby my diminutive body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:23.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, then, if that's the case,\nwhy don't you show me your powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:27.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! My greatest joy lies\nin making others unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These special...POWERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look now...if it pleases you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Target lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I just felt a chill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As if I were dumb enough to fall\nfor a 43-year-old trick like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I fell for a 33-year-old trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:09.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You pack a pretty good punch, don't\nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's just an ancient joke...{\i0}\NYou pack a pretty good punch, don't\nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's just an ancient joke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:21.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're pleased with the results?\NNeedless to say, I am totally happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:28.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By making my opponent miserable,\nmy wealth meter goes up, up, and away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:32.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Law of the\NConservation of Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish, I can generate\nmore unhappiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:40.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can win. With this demon\non my side, I can win at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's our real target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Make him miserable beyond belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:48.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:54.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You better brace yourself. Keiichi!\NBelldandy! Today's your last day\ntogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:03.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to tell the Goddess Belldandy\nwhat happened as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or else Megumi will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:13.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A walking stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to show this to my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're going in the opposite direction!{\i0}\nI've got to show this to my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's persimmon leaf tea,\nfrom the trees in our yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Persimmon leaf tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, there's a\ntea stalk floating upright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tea stalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:40.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's good luck when you see\na tea stalk standing up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So why do they say that it's good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:48.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...um...I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:52.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why don't we head\nover to the club house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:57.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting like a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance, Senbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:06.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,While I block Belldandy from seeing\nor sensing anything...possess Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:12.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! It's Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy isn't suspicious in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:23.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, you're not acting\nlike yourself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Kei-chan!\NYou must be imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're just like you always are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if Belldandy says so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:37.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Keiichi,\nyou're sharper than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:44.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what does it matter as long as\NBelldandy doesn't get wise to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:02.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I don't know why I even bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one is more suited for\nunhappiness than this young fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?\NYou get off me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! I'm really going\nto get pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:40.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, you're such a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:55.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you always were the type\nto do it anytime, anywhere, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in any kind of weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:00.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Megumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:03.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! This will send Keiichi's\nreputation right down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:08.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Keiichi's miserable, Belldandy will\nhave no choice but to return to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:13.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Victory! Victory is mine at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You threw yourself onto Sayoko\nto protect her from danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:27.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quite sure what happened\njust now, but thank you, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, were you mad at me, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:36.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what that\nwas all about just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be\nsunny out all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:50.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes it does matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Senbei, make sure you get\nthe job done next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:59.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me,\nI'll handle it at full throttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet sound of...shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:15.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad!\NAll right, let me do my part, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kei-chan, you're such a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:21.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you'd molest\nyour own sister right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:30.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you can't\nget anyone to date you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that's no reason to sink to\nthis subhuman level!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you've always\nlooked at me inappropriately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:41.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, Keiichi will\nbe labeled ''subhuman'', and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he won't be able to escape his misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That will force Belldandy to\nleave if nothing else will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure, victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:58.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you were trying to\nremove that insect from inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Megumi's shirt, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:07.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...you're not mad at me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:11.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as you're not, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:20.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Little Bear! Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Little Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way, Goddess Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:44.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All these weird things have\nbeen happening all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:50.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Changing clothes? Maybe it's Hasegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we wait, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Senbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:16:01.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If things go on like this, my pride will\nsuffer huge damage. Super-pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:03.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy, Senbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:30.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure...shower those\ntwo with misfortune and despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So now we're seeing\NKei-chan's true colors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:44.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Flirting with any girl he can get his hands\non. Girls are objects to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's in a lose-lose situation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He can't escape the onslaught of misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:53.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time for sure...\nvictory is really mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it, it's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, the pilot light went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to open\nthe windows right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just spaced out all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't come when you did,\nI really would've been in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to\NKeiichi's quick thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:24.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty scary\nwhen you get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:35.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know my happiness index\nshould be going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he must have a lot of happiness\ngushing out of him from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:46.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Keiichi was\nable to escape misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:50.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the source of that\nhappiness is...Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:53.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to seal her, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what kind of\ntest you had in mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...entering a vehicle with off-road\nspecs in a quarter-mile race...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...nobody would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fun in being conventional\nin a quarter-mile race?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:11.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,''Catch your opponents off balance!''\nis the motto of the Auto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And the incentive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll walk away with both the\nlaughs and the prize money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:35.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now's my chance! I'm going\nto hold back Belldandy's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:39.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Full Throttle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous...Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi\N{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:05.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calm yourself, Spirit of Fire!\NRetreat, Spirit of Air!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Goddess\NFirst Class Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:10.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...heed my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:20.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Spirits...\nplease put out that fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:24.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless.\NYour powers have been sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:26.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:28.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stuffed Bear Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:38.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess Belldandy...\NMarller has taken over Megumi's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she transformed me in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are you?{\i0}\NAnd she transformed me in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:45.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is I! The Earth Spirit who\nlives in Megumi's apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? You've been possessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers have been\nsealed by that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to believe\nwhat that stuffed animal says?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind him...what about Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if she finds out,\nshe can't attack me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This plan is absolutely failsafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goddess Belldandy!{\i0}\NThis plan is absolutely failsafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:10.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, there's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:14.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not Marller, then\nyou should be able to drink this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:18.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's tea with a tea stalk floating upright,\nit's good luck, like Keiichi said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:19.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back...back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're sending chills down my spine...\nI've got goose bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fire's going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fire's under control, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the full power\nof a First Class Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:02.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You cast a spell at full power\nto save me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:08.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...Keiichi...\nI was so afraid you'd be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd realized it was Marller...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:17.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you knew that Megumi\nwas acting strangely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:19.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I never...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:21.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:24.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure as a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to bring you happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:31.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't think I should\nbe near you, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:32.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have a goddess\nlike you by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:39.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never think of myself as unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The school racetrack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:54.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:01.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, why don't you come home with\nme?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a God of Poverty,\nyou worthless loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Don't pin the blame on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:14.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My work was flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:17.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I show you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:25.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.27,0:22:30.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and your\NDreams. You have a Wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:35.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:40.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:45.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:51.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:56.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:01.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:06.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:12.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:17.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.35,0:23:22.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:33.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:38.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:49.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:54.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Scars of the heart...a curse from\nthe past that can't be easily broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:03.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yet people learn to overcome all that,\nand move on towards the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:06.37,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! What Do Talent\nand Hard Work Have to Do With It?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:10.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's boot camp, but\ndoes she have to move in, too?
